      "content": "can you help me write a professional email to a customer? they ordered a really expensive espresso machine (the Breville Oracle Touch) but it's almost two weeks late because of a mistake in our warehouse logistics. i need to apologize, explain that it was a shipping error, and offer them a 20% discount on their next order to make it right. make it sound sincere but not too dramatic.",
