      "content": "Subject: Apology for Your Breville Oracle Touch Espresso Machine Delay\n\nDear [Customer's Name],\n\nI hope this email finds you well. I wanted to personally reach out to you regarding your recent order of the Breville Oracle Touch espresso machine. I understand that this machine is a significant investment, and we deeply regret the delay you've experienced.\n\nIt appears there was a miscommunication in our warehouse logistics, resulting in the shipping error. We are taking immediate steps to ensure this doesn't happen again in the future. As a token of our sincere apology, we would like to offer you a 20% discount on your next purchase with us. This discount will be automatically applied to your account, and we hope it helps to make up for the inconvenience.\n\nThank you for your understanding and patience. If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out. We value your business and look forward to serving you better in the future.\n\nWarm regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Your Contact Information]",
